{"tid":235340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公園唱歌果d大陸雞有無簽工作證？","createTime":"2017-05-09T02:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T10:04:53.000Z","uid":81397,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d684fb30711ecd08e97ced52e8311fc22e887c1f","tid":235340,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2018e3a65ba3f559c17df62e50b7d96fd0a59a9","tid":235340,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"他接收到的指引是，無論是否收錢，只要涉及外地表演者，一定要有工作簽證。"},{"pid":"b9cbd8b4d100dd4d167c8abad2c879b9f217adf0","tid":235340,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"係工廈又唔同玩法"},{"pid":"3f5af57fc2d328d5ff06e5db67f756cf8c53a0cc","tid":235340,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係工廈又唔同玩法</blockquote><br />\n他接收到的指引是，無論是否收錢，只要涉及外地表演者，一定要有工作簽證。"},{"pid":"eb21a2798eb715dd491a995cc965980d522bd6f5","tid":235340,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"舉報黑工熱線幾多號，我見到西洋菜街星期六日好多黑工賺錢"},{"pid":"2d36545370ec78056def4f2480ee0e0a14956cd4","tid":235340,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舉報黑工熱線幾多號，我見到西洋菜街星期六日好多黑工賺錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14537193029196945278572d98517d02731de27","tid":235340,"uid":76754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"